title: Choco. Mocha cake
description:
About Product:-

This mocha cake is moist, fluffy, and packed with chocolate and coffee flavor. Between each layer, you'll find a mocha buttercream, chocolate ganache, and chopped chocolate-covered espresso beans. This Chocolate Mocha Cake is extra rich and chocolatey with a silky mocha swiss meringue buttercream and dreamy chocolate ganache.
